# jemdoc: menu{MENU}{papers.html}, nofooter

= 发表论文

== MSA

1. [https://doi.org/10.1093/molbev/msac166 *HAlign 3*]: fast multiple alignment of ultra-large numbers of similar DNA/RNA sequences. *Molecular Biology and Evolution*. 2022 ([https://github.com/malabz/HAlign-3 soft])

2. [https://academic.oup.com/bioinformatics/article/40/12/btae718/7912339 *HAlign 4*]: a new strategy for rapidly aligning millions of sequences. *Bioinformatics*. 2024 ([https://github.com/malabz/HAlign-4 soft])

数据集推荐:适合处理序列数量极多、长度中等、整体相似度较高的数据集。

3. [https://doi.org/10.1093/bioinformatics/btae014 *FMAlign2*]: a novel fast multiple nucleotide sequence alignment method for ultralong datasets. *Bioinformatics*. 2024 ([https://github.com/malabz/FMAlign2 soft])

数据集推荐:适合序列数量少，但单条序列长度很长，且整体相似度较高的数据集。

4. [https://www.biorxiv.org/content/10.64898/2026.02.18.706716v1 *minipoa*]: A minimizer-based method for fast and memory-efficient partial order alignment. *biorixv*. 2026 ([https://github.com/NCl3-lhd/minipoa soft])

数据集推荐:适合序列数量中等，序列长度长，且整体相似度在中等以上的数据集。

== MSA post-processing

1. [https://doi.org/10.1371/journal.pcbi.1011988 *TPMA*]: A two pointers meta-alignment tool to ensemble different multiple nucleic acid sequence alignments. *PLOS COMPUTATIONAL BIOLOGY*. 2024 ([https://github.com/malabz/TPMA soft])

2. [https://academic.oup.com/nargab/article/6/4/lqae170/7928182 *ReAlign-N*]: an integrated realignment approach for multiple nucleic acid sequence alignment, combining global and local realignments. *NAR Genomics and Bioinformatics*. 2024 ([https://github.com/malabz/ReAlign-N soft])

== MGA

1. [https://doi.org/10.1101/gr.279763.124 Fast sequence alignment for centromere with RaMA]. *Genome Research*. 2025 ([https://github.com/metaphysicser/RaMA soft])

== PSA

1. [https://doi.org/10.1093/bib/bbaf061 *FORAlign*]: Accelerating gap-affine DNA pairwise sequence alignment using FOR-blocks based on FOur Russians approach with linear space complexity. *Briefings in Bioinformatics*. 2025 ([https://github.com/malabz/FORAlign soft])


== Review

1. [https://www.mdpi.com/2218-273X/12/4/546 Developments in Algorithms for Sequence Alignment]: A Review. *Biomolecules*. 2022

2. [https://doi.org/10.1093/bib/bbac069 A survey on the algorithm and development of multiple sequence alignment]. *Briefings in Bioinformatics*. 2022


== 其他论文

1. [https://academic.oup.com/bioinformatics/article/31/15/2475/188425 *HAlign*]: Fast multiple similar DNA/RNA sequence alignment based on the centre star strategy. *Bioinformatics*. 2015 ([https://github.com/malabz/HAlign soft])

2. [https://link.springer.com/content/pdf/10.1186/s13015-017-0116-x.pdf *HAlign 2*]: efficient ultra-large multiple sequence alignment and phylogenetic tree reconstruction with distributed and parallel computing. *Algorithms for Molecular Biology*. 2017 ([https://github.com/malabz/HAlign soft])

3. [https://academic.oup.com/bib/article/23/1/bbab519/6458932 *FMAlign*]: A novel fast multiple nucleotide sequence alignment method based on FM-index. *Briefings in Bioinformatics*. 2021

4. [https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/28646874/ *CMSA*]: a heterogeneous CPU\/GPU computing system for multiple similar RNA/DNA sequence alignment. *BMC Bioinformatics*. 2017 ([https://github.com/wangvsa/CMSA soft])

5. [https://link.springer.com/article/10.1186/s12918-017-0476-3 Reconstructing evolutionary trees in parallel for massive sequences]. *BMC Systems Biology*. 2017

6. [https://www.liebertpub.com/doi/10.1089/cmb.2017.0040 Multiple Sequence Alignment Based on a Suffix Tree and Center-Star Strategy]: A Linear Method for Multiple Nucleotide Sequence Alignment on Spark Parallel Framework. *Journal of Computational Biology*. 2017 ([https://github.com/suwenhecn/MASC soft])

7. [http://www.jgenetgenomics.org/en/article/doi/10.1016/j.jgg.2018.07.004 *VCSRA*]: A fast and accurate multiple sequence alignment algorithm with a high degree of parallelism. *Journal of Genetics and Genomics*. 2018 ([https://github.com/DongDongNeophyte/VCSRA_code soft])

8. [http://www.juestc.uestc.edu.cn/cn/article/doi/10.12178/1001-0548.2021406 Improved Center Star Alignment Algorithm Based on Profile Alignment]. *Journal of University of Electronic Science and Technology of China*. 2022

9. [https://doi.org/10.1093/bioinformatics/btac658 *WMSA*]: a novel method for multiple sequence alignment of DNA sequences. *Bioinformatics*. 2022 ([https://github.com/malabz/WMSA/ soft])

10. [https://doi.org/10.1093/bib/bbad190 *WMSA2*]: a multiple DNA/RNA sequence alignment tool implemented with accurate progressive mode and a fast win-win mode combining the center star and progressive strategies. *Briefings in Bioinformatics*. 2023 ([https://github.com/malabz/WMSA2/ soft])
